tga '''Tadrart''' yat tgrawt illan ɣ izzlmḍ n [[Agadir|ugadir]]. twala i tanbaḍt n imuzzar idawtanan, lli iḍfarn i tamnbaḍt n (u) [[Tamnbaḍt n Agadir-Idawtanan|Agadir-Idawtanan]].

ar gis ittwayskar yan ugadaz anmalass (ssuqq) kra ygat ass n usiḍyas (ssabt), d ar gis ittwayskar yan unmuggar lmusm n tdrart, ɣ tizi n unbdu (ṣṣiɣ) ɣ tigira n wayyur ɣuct.

tinafutin  n tadrart : amaris n tɣiwant, agadaz anmalass, timzgida, aggʷṛam (zzawit), tinml tamanzut, asinan n usmuttg, taddart n imḥdarn, ammas amsgnaf...

tissan tadrart s ussgmi n iggwlifn (tammant n tizzwa) zun-d akk tiqbilin yaḍnin n tmazirt n idawtanan.  

mad itggan audwwar, a s tammant n tizzwa (aggʷlif) zun-d akk tiqbilin n idawtanan. 

